\caption{Relative cell viability across four treatment conditions ($n=100$ per group).
Violin shapes show the kernel-density estimate of the distribution; overlaid box plots indicate the interquartile range and median (white line); individual observations are shown as jittered points ($\alpha=0.35$).
Significance brackets reflect pairwise Mann--Whitney $U$ tests with Bonferroni correction for five comparisons; $^{*}p<0.05$, $^{**}p<0.01$, $^{***}p<0.001$.}

